### Get all poems
GET http://localhost:7007/api/poem

### Get poem by ID
GET http://localhost:7007/api/poem/4

### Create a new poem
POST http://localhost:7007/api/poem
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Poem Title",
  "author": "Author Name",
  "content": "Put some poem content here...",
  "type": "VILLANELLE"
}

### Update a poem
PUT http://localhost:7007/api/poem/13
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated title",
  "author": "Updated Author",
  "content": "New poem content...",
  "type": "VILLANELLE"
}

### Delete a poem
DELETE http://localhost:7007/api/poem/3